title: Bring It S01E10 Miss D Breaks It Down WS DSR x264-[NY2] mp4
description:
Miss D will share some secrets and give us the history of hip hop majorettes...we'll get dish from the moms and girls on behind-the-scenes drama from the first nine episodes as well as performances by the Dancing Dolls, Baby Dolls, moms, and even Sunjai's dad JJ! Producers also plan to surprise Miss D and the girls with special celebrity shout-outs and guest appearances. This one-hour special will be hosted by Kim Coles.
